{
  "video_id": "Ziqq5gUXu8g",
  "title": "I Survived North Korea",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1370.0,
      "end_time": 3670.0,
      "text": "- I knew that if I was caught, I'll be killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4710.0,
      "end_time": 8000.0,
      "text": "I was born to a Chinese father and North Korean mother."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8000.0,
      "end_time": 10270.0,
      "text": "But when I was five, my father abandoned us"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10270.0,
      "end_time": 12020.0,
      "text": "and left to China and never returned."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12020.0,
      "end_time": 15690.0,
      "text": "I lost my mother six years later from starvation."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15690.0,
      "end_time": 17290.0,
      "text": "So I ended up living with my aunt"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 17290.0,
      "end_time": 21270.0,
      "text": "until my father sent my step-brother to take me to China."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21270.0,
      "end_time": 24480.0,
      "text": "So I ended up in my father's place in China in 2008."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24480.0,
      "end_time": 26310.0,
      "text": "Life in China was so much better."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26310.0,
      "end_time": 30170.0,
      "text": "I was so happy because I was living my life in freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30170.0,
      "end_time": 33130.0,
      "text": "But the happiness that I felt in China was only temporary"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 33130.0,
      "end_time": 35170.0,
      "text": "because Chinese government didn't recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35170.0,
      "end_time": 36840.0,
      "text": "North Koreans as refugees"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 36840.0,
      "end_time": 39950.0,
      "text": "and they deported back us to North Korea."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 39950.0,
      "end_time": 42040.0,
      "text": "The North Korean government wanted me to confess"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42040.0,
      "end_time": 44450.0,
      "text": "that I was trying to defect to South Korea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 44450.0,
      "end_time": 47650.0,
      "text": "but the truth was I went to China to find my father."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47650.0,
      "end_time": 50650.0,
      "text": "I had no desire to defect and begged them to understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50650.0,
      "end_time": 53320.0,
      "text": "I didn't confess, and after being for weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 53320.0,
      "end_time": 54910.0,
      "text": "they sent me to labor camp."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 54910.0,
      "end_time": 55993.0,
      "text": "I was only 15."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 57720.0,
      "end_time": 59490.0,
      "text": "In the labor camp, I was only allowed to eat"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 59490.0,
      "end_time": 62110.0,
      "text": "150 kernels of corn a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 62110.0,
      "end_time": 65110.0,
      "text": "One morning, we were marching in our rows to our work site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 65110.0,
      "end_time": 67723.0,
      "text": "and I saw a dry vomit on the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 68790.0,
      "end_time": 71500.0,
      "text": "I was so hungry that I got on my hands and knees"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 71500.0,
      "end_time": 74123.0,
      "text": "and began picking the rice out of the vomited rice."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76460.0,
      "end_time": 77950.0,
      "text": "I didn't stop eating the vomited rice"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 77950.0,
      "end_time": 81240.0,
      "text": "until the beating from the guards were too unbearable."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81240.0,
      "end_time": 83300.0,
      "text": "Eight months later, I was finally released"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 83300.0,
      "end_time": 86960.0,
      "text": "because I couldn't even stand up or even lift my arm."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 86960.0,
      "end_time": 89690.0,
      "text": "After spending months trying to regain my strength,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 89690.0,
      "end_time": 91480.0,
      "text": "I needed to find a job."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91480.0,
      "end_time": 93120.0,
      "text": "I began working in a coal mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 93120.0,
      "end_time": 95370.0,
      "text": "where I was paid only in rice."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 95370.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "Cave-ins were common, and I saw other boys"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100413.0,
      "text": "lose their arms and legs or else they were smashed"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100413.0,
      "end_time": 101930.0,
      "text": "into the rocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101930.0,
      "end_time": 103500.0,
      "text": "And I watched my friend die"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 103500.0,
      "end_time": 106440.0,
      "text": "when the coal cart fell off the track and crushed him."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 106440.0,
      "end_time": 108930.0,
      "text": "I worked in the mine about a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 108930.0,
      "end_time": 111060.0,
      "text": "and I realized it was my time"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 111060.0,
      "end_time": 112810.0,
      "text": "to try to escape North Korea again."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 114640.0,
      "end_time": 116730.0,
      "text": "I knew how hard escaping North Korea would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 116730.0,
      "end_time": 118973.0,
      "text": "without any money or food."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 120550.0,
      "end_time": 123050.0,
      "text": "And I knew that if I was caught, I will be killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 124040.0,
      "end_time": 127070.0,
      "text": "But those risks overweighted working in the dark coal mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 127070.0,
      "end_time": 132050.0,
      "text": "every day until it was my turn to lose a limb or die."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 132050.0,
      "end_time": 134300.0,
      "text": "One morning, instead of entering the mine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134300.0,
      "end_time": 136760.0,
      "text": "I walked up the path and began running."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136760.0,
      "end_time": 139110.0,
      "text": "I spent the next three months hiding from the police"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 139110.0,
      "end_time": 140520.0,
      "text": "and waiting for an opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140520.0,
      "end_time": 142540.0,
      "text": "to travel to the border town."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 142540.0,
      "end_time": 146200.0,
      "text": "On a humid day in August, I was lying down on a hillside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 146200.0,
      "end_time": 148610.0,
      "text": "and in the distance, I saw a train come to stop"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 148610.0,
      "end_time": 151250.0,
      "text": "and I realized the train was going to the border town,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 151250.0,
      "end_time": 154603.0,
      "text": "and as the passengers boarded again, I joined the line."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 156610.0,
      "end_time": 159770.0,
      "text": "And the guard would ask for my papers and documents"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 159770.0,
      "end_time": 162510.0,
      "text": "and I lied that my mother had them"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 162510.0,
      "end_time": 164783.0,
      "text": "and that she was already on the train."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 166660.0,
      "end_time": 168020.0,
      "text": "He nodded and I headed"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 168020.0,
      "end_time": 170020.0,
      "text": "straight for the train bathroom to hide."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 172490.0,
      "end_time": 175470.0,
      "text": "I spent the next two days hiding from the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 175470.0,
      "end_time": 177100.0,
      "text": "I was almost at the border town"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 177100.0,
      "end_time": 179320.0,
      "text": "when the hands of a guard grabbed the back of my neck"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 179320.0,
      "end_time": 181670.0,
      "text": "and dragged me to a holding cell on the train."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 181670.0,
      "end_time": 185150.0,
      "text": "I thought about how terrible the labor camp had been,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 185150.0,
      "end_time": 187560.0,
      "text": "the long days of manual labor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 187560.0,
      "end_time": 190600.0,
      "text": "sleepless nights that spent memorizing the rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 190600.0,
      "end_time": 192713.0,
      "text": "and the constant feelings of hunger."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 193850.0,
      "end_time": 195280.0,
      "text": "I refused to let that happen again."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 195280.0,
      "end_time": 198430.0,
      "text": "Once the train began to slow down for the next stop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 198430.0,
      "end_time": 201350.0,
      "text": "I saw a window was unlocked so I pushed it open"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 201350.0,
      "end_time": 203550.0,
      "text": "and squeezed out of the small opening."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 203550.0,
      "end_time": 206470.0,
      "text": "I jumped off the moving train and rolled into a ditch"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 206470.0,
      "end_time": 209610.0,
      "text": "and began sprinting for some nearby trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 209610.0,
      "end_time": 212590.0,
      "text": "I ran for hours, illegally boarded a second train,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 212590.0,
      "end_time": 215460.0,
      "text": "and two days later, I finally made it to the border town."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 215460.0,
      "end_time": 218360.0,
      "text": "I walked into the river that divides North Korea and China"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 219380.0,
      "end_time": 221780.0,
      "text": "and I hid in the tall grass for eight hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 221780.0,
      "end_time": 223420.0,
      "text": "waiting for the darkness."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 223420.0,
      "end_time": 224760.0,
      "text": "When I finally thought it was safe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 224760.0,
      "end_time": 226710.0,
      "text": "I quietly waded into the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 226710.0,
      "end_time": 229040.0,
      "text": "In the middle of the river, I slipped on a rock"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 229040.0,
      "end_time": 230333.0,
      "text": "and let out a scream."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 231530.0,
      "end_time": 233980.0,
      "text": "Immediately, a floodlight was on my back"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 233980.0,
      "end_time": 235780.0,
      "text": "and I heard a guard screaming at me."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 237070.0,
      "end_time": 240370.0,
      "text": "He said that he would shoot me if I didn't turn back."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 240370.0,
      "end_time": 242400.0,
      "text": "I knew that I was dead either way."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 242400.0,
      "end_time": 245230.0,
      "text": "Either he would shoot me or I would obey"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 245230.0,
      "end_time": 248493.0,
      "text": "and return to shore, only to be shipped off to labor camp."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 250690.0,
      "end_time": 252283.0,
      "text": "I decided not to turn back."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 253280.0,
      "end_time": 256020.0,
      "text": "Each step took me further away from North Korea"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 256019.99999999997,
      "end_time": 257719.99999999997,
      "text": "and closer to my dream of freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 258600.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260840.00000000003,
      "text": "And five minutes later, I was dripping wet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 260839.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262353.0,
      "text": "but finally back in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 263240.0,
      "end_time": 265110.0,
      "text": "I walked in China for three days"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 265110.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "until somebody found me collapsed in the middle of a road."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 272353.0,
      "text": "I was hungry and I was dehydrated and I was exhausted."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 273580.0,
      "end_time": 274870.0,
      "text": "When the man that found me"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 274870.0,
      "end_time": 276960.0,
      "text": "realized that I was from North Korea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 276960.0,
      "end_time": 279650.0,
      "text": "he helped me to make a contact with the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 279650.0,
      "end_time": 282160.0,
      "text": "who helped me to come to Southeast Asia"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 282160.0,
      "end_time": 285090.0,
      "text": "where I was processed to come to the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 285090.0,
      "end_time": 286413.0,
      "text": "I remember looking out the window"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 286413.0,
      "end_time": 288683.0,
      "text": "once the plane began to land in California."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 289890.0,
      "end_time": 292960.0,
      "text": "I've never dreamed of being on a plane"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 292960.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "or even coming to America."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 295700.0,
      "end_time": 298560.0,
      "text": "And as I step off the plane, I felt this strange feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 298560.0,
      "end_time": 300010.0,
      "text": "that I've never known before."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 301250.0,
      "end_time": 302520.0,
      "text": "Safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 302520.0,
      "end_time": 305333.0,
      "text": "I was finally safe and I didn't need to hide anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 306470.0,
      "end_time": 308380.0,
      "text": "And I came to America five years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 308380.0,
      "end_time": 310490.0,
      "text": "and in that time, I have learned English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 310490.0,
      "end_time": 313420.0,
      "text": "graduate from high school, worked as a sushi chef."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 313420.0,
      "end_time": 316210.0,
      "text": "My life in America has not been easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 316210.0,
      "end_time": 318630.0,
      "text": "but this is land of opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 318630.0,
      "end_time": 321623.0,
      "text": "and I know that if I work hard, I can achieve my dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 324090.0,
      "end_time": 326653.0,
      "text": "And today, I stand here as the exception."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 327780.0,
      "end_time": 330793.0,
      "text": "For every story about a North Korean like mine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 331670.0,
      "end_time": 333810.0,
      "text": "thousands of others end in tragedy."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 336040.0,
      "end_time": 337940.0,
      "text": "And sometimes, I wonder why it was me."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 339850.0,
      "end_time": 341880.0,
      "text": "Why was I the one that survived in the labor camp"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 341880.0,
      "end_time": 343440.0,
      "text": "and my cellmates starved to death?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 343440.0,
      "end_time": 344930.0,
      "text": "And why did the coal cart fall off"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 344930.0,
      "end_time": 346670.0,
      "text": "the other side of the rails,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 346670.0,
      "end_time": 348710.0,
      "text": "crushing my friend instead of me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 348710.0,
      "end_time": 351600.0,
      "text": "And why did I get a chance to jump off the train"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 351600.0,
      "end_time": 353200.0,
      "text": "and those two other boys didn't?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 354230.0,
      "end_time": 357140.0,
      "text": "I struggled with this questions for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 357140.0,
      "end_time": 359270.0,
      "text": "And the small gift that I can give"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 359270.0,
      "end_time": 362543.0,
      "text": "to those that are not here today is to share my story."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 364440.0,
      "end_time": 365273.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    }
  ]
}